    @GenAsPersistable(interfaces={WTContained.class,Identified.class},
                  extendable=true,
                  foreignKeys=@GeneratedForeignKey(name="IdentifiedContainerLink",foreignKeyRole=@ForeignKeyRole(name="container",type=WTContainer.class,supportedAPI=PRIVATE,cascade=false,constraints=@PropertyConstraints(changeable=VIA_OTHER_MEANS,required=true)),myRole=@MyRole(name="contents",supportedAPI=PRIVATE)))
public interface WTContainedIdentified
    A utitlity interface that objects that are both Identified and WTContained should implement. This interface forces callers to use IdentityService.changeIdentity to change an object's container reference, as opposed to WTContained.setContainerReference.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
    See Also:
    WTContainerNamespace, WTContained, Identified, IdentityService#changeIdentity, IdentityHelper#isChangeable
